<p>9.1 =E2=80=93 Workforce Management UKG/Kronos: Following points were add=
ed for FC01 (Kronos) 1) SailPoint to support manual request provisioning/de=
-provisioning and 2) Segregation Of Duties (SOD) validation will be support=
ed by SailPoint</p>
<p>9.2 =E2=80=93 ServiceNow: Following points were added for FC02(ServiceNo=
w): 1) SailPoint IIQ shall be source of truth for account and access operat=
ions performed in ServiceNow, 2) SailPoint to support manual request provis=
ioning/de-provisioning and 3) SOD validation will be supported by SailPoint=
</p>
<p>9.5 =E2=80=93 Oracle Enterprise Performance Management Cloud (Oracle EPM=
