oud module connector details and 2) SOD validation will be supported by Sai=
lPoint</p>
<p>9.6 =E2=80=93 Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI): Following points were a=
dded for OCI: 1) SOD validation will be supported by SailPoint</p>
